message: Hi Bob, I have a product that I believe would be of great interest to you. I'm offering it to you today for $25000. Let me know if you're interested!
Hi Alice, thank you for your offer! Unfortunately, $25000 is beyond my budget for this product. I can offer you $10000 instead. Let me know if that works for you.
I appreciate your offer, Bob, but $10000 is too low for what this product is worth. I can come down to $20000. I believe this is a fair price given the quality and value of the product.
